java.lang.Object
com.remotehealth.app.model.User
com.remotehealth.app.model.Doctor
public class Doctor extends User
DOCTOR CLASS Represents a doctor user in the system with patient management capabilities. Extends the base User class and adds doctor-specific functionality.
